OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1774379485
OL,3,CSnooker World Championship staying at
OL,4,CSheffield Crucible until at least 2045
OL,6,FSheffield will continue to host the
OL,7,FSnooker World Championships until at
OL,8,Fleast 2045 as major refurbishment
OL,9,Fplans are announced for the Crucible
OL,10,FTheatre.
OL,12,FThe landmark long-term agreement
OL,13,Fbetween World Snooker Tour and
OL,14,FSheffield City Council will see the
OL,15,Fcompetition remain in the Steel City
OL,16,Ffor the next 19 years, with an option
OL,17,Fto extend to 2050.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
