OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1774379485
OL,3,CSnooker World Championship staying at
OL,4,CSheffield Crucible until at least 2045
OL,6,FSnooker's flagship event first came to
OL,7,Fthe Crucible in 1977 and will
OL,8,Fcelebrate its 50th anniversary at the
OL,9,Ficonic venue next year.
OL,11,FSeparately, plans are being developed
OL,12,Fto transform the Crucible Theatre,
OL,13,Fincluding the potential to add up to
OL,14,F500 additional seats in an 'in the
OL,15,Fround' configuration.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
