OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1774379485
OL,3,CSnooker World Championship staying at
OL,4,CSheffield Crucible until at least 2045
OL,6,FCommenting on the announcement, Leader
OL,7,Fof Sheffield City Council, Cllr Tom
OL,8,FHunt said: "Sheffield loves snooker `
OL,9,Fand it's here to stay. We've reached
OL,10,Fan agreement to keep the World Snooker
OL,11,FChampionship at the Crucible, the home
OL,12,Fof snooker, supporting its future in
OL,13,Four city."
OL,15,FThe Championship will continue to be
OL,16,Fstaged at the Crucible in its current
OL,17,Fdesign through to 2028. During the
OL,18,Frefurbishment, the event is expected
OL,19,Fto be hosted temporarily at an
OL,20,Falternative venue before returning to
OL,21,Fa transformed Crucible.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
