OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1774379485
OL,3,CSnooker World Championship staying at
OL,4,CSheffield Crucible until at least 2045
OL,6,FThis year's Halo World Championship
OL,7,Fruns from 18 April to 4 May, as the
OL,8,Fworld's top 16 players and 16
OL,9,Fqualifiers gather to compete for a
OL,10,Ftrophy first contested in 1927,
OL,11,Falongside a top prize of #500,000. The
OL,12,Fevent has a global cumulative audience
OL,13,Fof 771 million.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
