PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1774379485
OL,3,CSnooker World Championship staying at
OL,4,CSheffield Crucible until at least 2045
OL,6,FWorld Snooker Tour Chairman Steve
OL,7,FDawson said: "This is the news that
OL,8,Fplayers and fans around the world have
OL,9,Fbeen waiting and hoping for. It comes
OL,10,Ffollowing years of close negotiation
OL,11,Fwith Sheffield City Council and the UK
OL,12,FGovernment and we are delighted to
OL,13,Fhave reached this far-reaching
OL,14,Fagreement."
OL,26,@oD@NOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
