PN,36306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1774379485
OL,3,CSnooker World Championship staying at
OL,4,CSheffield Crucible until at least 2045
OL,6,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer, said: "We
OL,7,Fhave a deep cultural and sporting
OL,8,Fheritage here in the UK - sport, art
OL,9,Fand culture are the very best of us.
OL,10,FIt's what makes us proud not only of
OL,11,Fthe country, but the places that we're
OL,12,Ffrom."
OL,14,FSnooker legend Stephen Hendry, said:
OL,15,F"There is simply nowhere else like the
OL,16,FCrucible or anywhere else that could
OL,17,Freplicate that atmosphere or the sense
OL,18,Fof history. It was always my favourite
OL,19,Fplace to play and I still love going
OL,20,Fto Sheffield. "
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
